content: Hi, I wanted to join the rustc source reading club which is taking place right now, but 1. when I try to join the zoom meeting linked in the calendar invite (https://zoom.us/j/91466548113?pwd=TXRweGdqQ3JtWWVwd1BMZUxWcHJBQT09) it says that the meeting has reached its capacity 2. the website appears to be gone https://rust-code-reading-club.github.io/rustc. @nikomatsakis @Doc Jones what's going on?
We're switching to another platform because of the meeting capacity limit. I think the details will be posted in #rustc-reading-club.
thanks, I didn't know there was a dedicated channel for that :)
